與大部分慢車地鐵站相同，泉街設有兩個側式月台和四條軌道。兩個中央快車軌道由在日間由[[紐約地鐵A線|A線]]列車使用。一條閘內的下通道容許反方向轉乘。

=== 出口 ===
所有閘機區都位於月台層。車站的主要閘機位於月台南端。各個閘機包括標準的轉棍閘機、一個票務處以及一條通往泉街及第六大道的樓梯。北行側的出口建於學校大樓內，並前往東北角；而南行側前往西北角<ref name=maps/>。南行月台設有無職員駐守的閘機，並設有一條樓梯前往范達姆街及第六大道西南角<ref name=maps>{{cite web|title=MTA Neighborhood Maps: SoHo / Tribeca|url=http://web.mta.info/maps/neighborhoods/mn/M02_SoHo_TriBeCa_2015.pdf|publisher=[[大都會運輸署|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=2015-08-06|date=2015|archive-date=2020-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200914204436/http://web.mta.info/maps/neighborhoods/mn/M02_SoHo_TriBeCa_2015.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此站北端還設有已關閉的閘機區，並前往王子街/查爾頓街及第六大道的全部四個角落<ref name=MTA-ReviewAC-2015>{{cite web|title=Review of the A and C Lines|url=http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/pdf/AC_LineReview.pdf|publisher=[[大都會運輸署|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=2016-01-19|date=2015-12-11}}</ref>。

==藝術 ==
[[File:Spring_Street_Mosaic.jpg|thumb]]車站月台]]
1984年12月，智利藝術家{{link-en|阿尔弗雷多·贾尔|Alfredo Jaar}}租下了車站內所有的廣告空間一個月，並安裝了他稱為「Rushes」的物品，顯示81張他拍攝貧窮的巴西工人在政府營運的[[金礦|金礦]]{{link-en|露天山|Serra Pelada}}挖掘的照片。在他們之間散佈的為顯示[[油價|世界油價]]<ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=kr40kS6yK1AC&pg=PA214&dq=%22spring+street%22+ind+station+-atlanta&hl=en&sa=X&ei=NCgdUde_K8bJ0QGwgYGYDg&ved=0CEcQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=%22spring%20street%22%20ind%20station%20-atlanta&f=false |title=Subway City: Riding the Trains, Reading New York |author=Michael W. Brooks |publisher= |date= |accessdate=2013-02-14 |archive-date=2017-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170417084419/https://books.google.com/books?id=kr40kS6yK1AC&pg=PA214&dq=%22spring+street%22+ind+station+-atlanta&hl=en&sa=X&ei=NCgdUde_K8bJ0QGwgYGYDg&ved=0CEcQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=%22spring%20street%22%20ind%20station%20-atlanta&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hYROgc2s2DgC&pg=PA271&dq=%22spring+street%22+ind+station+-atlanta&hl=en&sa=X&ei=NCgdUde_K8bJ0QGwgYGYDg&ved=0CE8Q6AEwBg#v=onepage&q=%22spring%20street%22&f=false |title=Art and the Subway: New York Underground |author=Tracy Fitzpatrick |publisher= |date=2009-05-30 |accessdate=2013-02-14 |archive-date=2017-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170417082526/https://books.google.com/books?id=hYROgc2s2DgC&pg=PA271&dq=%22spring+street%22+ind+station+-atlanta&hl=en&sa=X&ei=NCgdUde_K8bJ0QGwgYGYDg&ved=0CE8Q6AEwBg#v=onepage&q=%22spring%20street%22&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/newsday/access/100891589.html?dids=100891589:100891589&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Dec+04%2C+1986&author=By+Jim+Dwyer&pub=Newsday+%28Combined+editions%29&desc=IN+THE+SUBWAYSA+Little+Digging+Yields+Clues+to+the+Revolution&pqatl=google |author= |title=IN THE SUBWAYS; A Little Digging Yields Clues to the Revolution |publisher= |date= |accessdate=2013-02-15}}</ref>。

1994年藝術則安裝在車站北行月台閘機的樓梯上，是一個大型的馬賽克，名為《紐約市地鐵站》（{{lang|en|New York City Subway Station}}），由Edith Kramer創作<ref name="wordpress1">{{cite web |url=https://ephemeralnewyork.wordpress.com/tag/subway-station-art/ |author= |title=subway station art |publisher=Ephemeral New York |date= |accessdate=2013-02-15 |archive-date=2018-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005091928/https://ephemeralnewyork.wordpress.com/tag/subway-station-art/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其包括一幅畫顯示[[IRT萊辛頓大道線|IRT萊辛頓大道線]]的[[14街-聯合廣場車站_(IRT萊辛頓大道線)|14街-聯合廣場車站]]<ref name="wordpress1"/>。

